The Riddle of Steel - Combat Companion

This is a little interactive game aid for The Riddle of Steel pen & paper role-playing game.  For the hosted version, please visit: http://riddleofsteel.heroku.com/

For more about The Riddle of Steel, try Wikipedia (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Riddle_of_Steel) or the now defunct homepage (http://www.driftwoodpublishing.com/).